BlankApplication Extension OpenERP Connector
==========

BA Extension OpenERP is a plugin to handle remote connection to OpenERP
Of course, You need to have a remote OpenERP instance running.
This plugin let you configure an OpenERP Connection

Dependencies
=======

This plugin is based on Ooor gem distributed on http://github.com/rvalyi/ooor
just run: sudo gem install ooor

Install
=======

Simply run:
rake openerp:install

